## Step 1 – Authentication (MVP-1: Core + MVP-2: Enhancements)

### MVP-1 Goals
- PostgreSQL `users` table with hashed passwords (Argon2)
- `POST /api/auth/login` → returns JWT access token
- `GET /api/auth/me` → returns current user info
- Auto-seed `admin` user at startup if none exists
- Frontend login page, `AuthContext`, and protected route wrapper

### MVP-2 Enhancements (after MVP-1 is stable)
- Refresh tokens with sliding expiry stored in DB
- `POST /api/auth/logout` with server-side token invalidation
- Rate limiting on `/api/auth/login` endpoint (via `slowapi`)
- HTTPS cookie transport in production

