## Step 2 – Authorization / RBAC (MVP-1: Role Guards + MVP-2: Contract-Level Permissions)

### MVP-1 Goals
- Four roles: `admin`, `reviewer`, `approver`, `viewer`
- Every existing API endpoint annotated with `require_role(...)` dependency
- Admin-only: create/list/update/deactivate users
- Frontend: hide/disable actions based on role

### MVP-2 Enhancements
- Contract-level ownership/assignment checks (only assigned reviewers can review a contract)
- Audit trail for permission denials stored to PG `access_audit_log` table
- Team-based roles (e.g., `reviewer:team_a`)

